`guild().config<OculusConfig>('oculus')` → reads `guild.json["oculus"]`

### Existing `consumes` tokens in the codebase

- `'tools'` — consumed by Instrumentarium
- `'roles'` — consumed by Loom

The Oculus introduces: `'pages'` and `'routes'`

